[...]

If Foxes Fox were a rock band, it would doubtless be labeled a &quot;super group&quot; as
all four members are among the very best players on their instruments. However,
this is an improvising group so any notions of &quot;stars&quot; must be dispelled in
favor of collective music making and interaction. The quartet delivers exactly
that right from the start. At almost 39 minutes, the opening track, &quot;Foxes Set
1,&quot; represents their first set of the evening and the four demonstrate
